  "reviews": "\u201cI can't believe how fun this game is...I really really like it...I highly, highly recommend it\u201d<br>Wil Wheaton (on the physical version of Hive)<br><br>\u201cI'm a really big fan of Hive\u201d<br>Jerry Holkins (TychoBrahe from Penny Arcade on the physical version of Hive)<br><br>\u201cSo let it be said that Hive, a simple adaption of a cult board game, is the game that ended the Leaderboard\u2019s losing streak.\u201d<br>Approved \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://indiegamerchick.com/2013/05/30/h-i-v-e/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Indie Gamer Chick</a><br>",
